---
import vic1 from '@assets/images/about/vicmac1.jpg';
import {Image} from "astro:assets";
---
<section class="container mb-12">
    <div class="profile-section">
        <Image transition:name="profile-picture" class="profile-picture" src={vic1} alt="cover of victor alvarado" loading={"eager"}/>
        <div>
            <p>
                🤚🏻 Hi! I'm Victor Alvarado, a software engineer and full-stack developer from Honduras 🇭🇳,
                a small country in Central America.
            </p>
            <p>
                I've been building software professionally since 2015 — over a decade of shipping products across
                web, mobile, and SaaS platforms.
            </p>
            <p>
                Along the way I've worn a lot of hats: UI designer, frontend developer, backend developer,
                Android developer, and full-stack developer. Curiosity is what pushed me across all of them —
                I learn best by building.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>
        I don't claim to be an expert in everything I've touched, but I carry real experience from each role —
        lessons from the projects that worked and the ones that didn't.
    </p>
    <p class="text-highlight">
        These days I'm focused on product engineering with <b>Next.js, TypeScript, React, Supabase, PostgreSQL,
        and OpenAI</b> — shipping features end-to-end for remote teams.
    </p>
</section>

<style>
    .profile-section {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        flex-direction: column; /* Default to column for mobile */
    }

    .profile-picture {
        width: 150px;
        height: auto;
        filter: grayscale(1);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .profile-section {
            flex-direction: row; /* Change to row for desktop */
        }

        .profile-picture {
            width: 300px;
        }
    }
</style>